Hoboken.Central Avenue (Hudson Palisades): Central Avenue in Jersey City Heights is the main commercial thoroughfare for that section of Jersey City, New Jersey, USA, and is designated County Route 663 for 1.60-mile (2.57 km) of its length. It runs just north of Newark Avenue near Five Corners to Paterson Plank Road near Transfer Station. The avenue continues north through Union City without the county route designation to 35th Street (CR 674), two blocks norrth of Hackensack Plank Road.
